tests
deploy
README*.md
DEPLOY*.md
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md

# Legacy internal UIs — kept in the repo for local dev / demos but excluded
# from the production image so Flask's static handler can't serve them even
# if Caddy ever mis-routes. Caddy still 404's these paths as belt+suspenders.
web/app.html
web/admin.html
